  <h1>Titanium vs Ceramic Cookware: Which Should You Choose?</h1>
  <p><time datetime='2025-10-02'>Last updated October 2, 2025</time></p>
  <p class='disclosure note'>We test and recommend cookware. If you buy via links on this page, we may earn a commission at no cost to you. Links are marked and follow FTC guidance.</p>
</header>

